outfit_data.top: A cream-colored silk blouse with a relaxed, empire waist silhouette. The blouse features delicate smocking details at the neckline and sleeves for a touch of elegance.
outfit_data.bottom: Khaki linen pants in an A-line style. They are tailored for a flattering fit but retain a breezy, comfortable feel suitable for a beach setting.
outfit_data.shoes: Nude suede heeled sandals with a thin strap that wraps around the ankle. The heel is mid-height for both comfort and style.
outfit_data.extras: A woven straw tote bag in a natural color to carry essentials. A lightweight camel-colored wool cardigan can be draped over the shoulders for cooler evenings.
